lang="ru">Восходит <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>*han-kār-</w></mentioned>, ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>angārdan</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w>angarīdan: angār-</w> <gloss><q>размышлять</q></gloss></mentioned>, , ‘предполагать’, ‘думать’, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/> <w>hangārtan</w> <gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘иметь в виду’, ‘принимать в расчет’, ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>%r2%rkar-</w> <gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘воспринимать’ (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_AiW"/><biblScope>449</biblScope></bibl>). Неожиданное появление смычно-гортанного %ikʼ%i наводит на мысль, не имела ли места контаминация с каким-нибудь иноязычным словом. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="mn"><lang/> <w>anqar-</w> <gloss><q>воспринимать</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>*han-kār-</w></mentioned>, ср. <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/> <w>angārdan</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang=""><w>angarīdan: angār-</w> <gloss><q>to reflect</q></gloss></mentioned>, , ‘to suppose’, ‘to think’, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/> <w>hangārtan</w> <gloss><q>to remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘to mean’, ‘to take into consideration’, compare <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>%r2%rkar-</w> <gloss><q>to remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘to perceive’ (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_AiW"/><biblScope>449</biblScope></bibl>). Unexpected appearance of ejective consonant %ikʼ%i suggests the assumption of the contamination with some foreign word. Compare <mentioned xml:lang="mn"><lang/> <w>anqar-</w> <gloss><q>to perceive</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>